text: Robert Boyd Holbrook (born September 1, 1981) is an American actor and fashion model. He is known for his roles in Milk, Out of the Furnace, Run All Night, A Walk Among the Tombstones, Gone Girl, A Complete Unknown and starred as DEA Agent Steve Murphy in Netflix series Narcos.
